AUDIO: 'This is Superpowers, the agentic skills framework with more than 50,000 stars on GitHub that stops your coding agents from rushing and making mistakes by forcing it through a structured workflow that contains brainstorming, implementation, red-green test-driven'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'development, and even using sub-agents to execute tasks and review code in parallel. But, what makes this different from just using plan mode or something like spec-driven development? Hit subscribe and let\'s get into it.'

[00:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'So, this is a project called XDL, which is a CLI tool used to download videos from Twitter. I want to create a web UI for this tool that not only downloads videos to the user\'s browser from a URL,'

