VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'tweet. Sorry, Kevin. Paste it here and see if it\'ll download the video. So, it\'s extracting and it\'s been able to download it. So, if I click here, it opens it in a new tab, which is not what I expected, but hey, it does the thing.'

[01:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
